trans-unit.source: Defines a rectangular hot spot region in an <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: Define uma região de ponto de acesso retangular em uma <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap"> </xref> controle.

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: Essa classe não pode ser herdada.

trans-unit.source: This class defines a rectangular hot spot region in an <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap> control.
trans-unit.target: Essa classe define uma região de ponto de acesso retangular em uma <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap>controle.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap>

trans-unit.source: To define the region of the RectangleHotSpot object, set the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.RectangleHotSpot.Left%2A> property to the value that represents the x-coordinate of the rectangular region's top left corner.
trans-unit.target: Para definir a região do objeto RectangleHotSpot, defina o <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.RectangleHotSpot.Left%2A>canto esquerdo de propriedade para o valor que representa a coordenada x do início da região retangular.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.RectangleHotSpot.Left%2A>

trans-unit.source: Set the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.RectangleHotSpot.Top%2A> property to the value that represents the y-coordinate of the rectangular region's top left corner.
trans-unit.target: Definir o <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.RectangleHotSpot.Top%2A>canto esquerdo de propriedade para o valor que representa a coordenada y do início da região retangular.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.RectangleHotSpot.Top%2A>

trans-unit.source: Set the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.RectangleHotSpot.Right%2A> property to the value that represents the x-coordinate of the rectangular region's bottom right corner.
trans-unit.target: Definir o <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.RectangleHotSpot.Right%2A>propriedade para o valor que representa a coordenada x do canto direito inferior da região retangular.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.RectangleHotSpot.Right%2A>

trans-unit.source: Set of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.RectangleHotSpot.Bottom%2A> property to the value that represents the y-coordinate of the rectangular region's bottom right corner.
trans-unit.target: Conjunto do <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.RectangleHotSpot.Bottom%2A>propriedade para o valor que representa a coordenada y do canto direito inferior da região retangular.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.RectangleHotSpot.Bottom%2A>

trans-unit.source: When a RectangleHotSpot control is clicked, the page navigates to a URL, generates a post back to the server, or does nothing.
trans-unit.target: Quando um controle RectangleHotSpot é clicado, a página navega para um URL, gera uma postagem para o servidor ou não faz nada.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.HotSpotMode%2A> property specifies this behavior.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.HotSpotMode%2A>propriedade especifica esse comportamento.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.HotSpotMode%2A>

trans-unit.source: To navigate to a URL, set the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.HotSpotMode%2A> property to `HotSpotMode.Navigate` and use the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.NavigateUrl%2A> property to specify the URL to navigate to.
trans-unit.target: Para navegar até uma URL, defina o <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.HotSpotMode%2A>propriedade `HotSpotMode.Navigate` e usar o <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.NavigateUrl%2A>propriedade para especificar a URL de navegação.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.NavigateUrl%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.HotSpotMode%2A>

trans-unit.source: To post back to the server, set the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.HotSpotMode%2A> property to `HotSpotMode.PostBack` and use the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.PostBackValue%2A> property to specify a name for the RectangleHotSpot object.
trans-unit.target: Para lançar no servidor, defina o <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.HotSpotMode%2A>propriedade `HotSpotMode.PostBack` e usar o <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.PostBackValue%2A>propriedade para especificar um nome para o objeto RectangleHotSpot.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.PostBackValue%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.HotSpotMode%2A>

trans-unit.source: This name will be passed in the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMapEventArgs> event data when the RectangleHotSpot is clicked.
trans-unit.target: Esse nome será passado a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMapEventArgs>dados de evento quando o RectangleHotSpot é clicado.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMapEventArgs>

trans-unit.source: If you want the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot> object to have no behavior, set the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.HotSpotMode%2A> property to `HotSpotMode.Inactive`.
trans-unit.target: Se você quiser que o <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot>objeto não ter nenhum comportamento, defina o <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.HotSpotMode%2A>propriedade `HotSpotMode.Inactive`.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.HotSpotMode%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot>

trans-unit.target: Obtém ou define a coordenada y do lado inferior da região retangular definida por este <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.RectangleHotSpot"> </xref> objeto.

trans-unit.source: Returns a string that represents the x -and y-coordinates of a <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.RectangleHotSpot"></xref> object's top left corner and the x- and y-coordinates of its bottom right corner.
trans-unit.target: Retorna uma cadeia de caracteres que representa o x- e y de um <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.RectangleHotSpot"> </xref> superior do objeto esquerdo canto e as coordenadas x e y de seu inferior canto direito.

trans-unit.source: This method returns a string that represents the coordinates of a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.RectangleHotSpot> object's top left corner and the coordinates of its bottom right corner.
trans-unit.target: Esse método retorna uma cadeia de caracteres que representa as coordenadas de um <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.RectangleHotSpot>superior do objeto esquerdo canto e as coordenadas do seu inferior canto direito.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.RectangleHotSpot>

trans-unit.source: This method uses the values assigned to the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.RectangleHotSpot.Left%2A> and <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.RectangleHotSpot.Top%2A> properties to return the coordinates for the top left corner.
trans-unit.target: Esse método usa os valores atribuídos ao <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.RectangleHotSpot.Left%2A>e <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.RectangleHotSpot.Top%2A>Propriedades para retornar as coordenadas da parte superior esquerda.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.RectangleHotSpot.Top%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.RectangleHotSpot.Left%2A>

trans-unit.source: It uses the values assigned to the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.RectangleHotSpot.Right%2A> and <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.RectangleHotSpot.Bottom%2A> properties to return the coordinates for the bottom right corner.
trans-unit.target: Ele usa os valores atribuídos ao <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.RectangleHotSpot.Right%2A>e <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.RectangleHotSpot.Bottom%2A>Propriedades para retornar as coordenadas para a parte inferior direita canto.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.RectangleHotSpot.Bottom%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.RectangleHotSpot.Right%2A>

trans-unit.source: The GetCoordinates method is used internally by ASP.NET to get the text to use for the coordinates of a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.RectangleHotSpot> when it is rendered.
trans-unit.target: O método GetCoordinates é usado internamente pelo ASP.NET para obter o texto a ser usado para as coordenadas de um <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.RectangleHotSpot>quando ele for renderizado.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.RectangleHotSpot>

trans-unit.source: The string that is returned is specific to the browser and markup language.
trans-unit.target: A cadeia de caracteres que é retornada é específica para o idioma do navegador e marcação.
